==English==
[[Image:Pregnant belly button.jpg|thumb|right|The belly of a pregnant woman.]]

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|beli}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|bælġ}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*balgiz}}. Compare German {{m|de|Balg}}, Dutch {{m|nl|balg}}. Probably ultimately from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*bhle-||to swell, blow up}}. See also {{m|en|bellows}}.

